What is it?
~~~~~~~~~~~
QmailAdmin is a cgi program for administering Qmail with vchkpw.

Requirements:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- A UNIX computer (Linux/Solaris/BSD) and C compiler (gcc)

- A web server (Apache, Zeus)
    http://www.apache.org/

- (S)Qmail
    http://cr.yp.to/qmail.html 
    https://www.fehcom.de/sqmail/sqmail.html

- vpopmail (a virtual domain addon for qmail) 
    http://www.inter7.com/vpopmail/

- ezmlm installed in /usr/local/bin/ezmlm 
    http://cr.yp.to/ezmlm.html
    http://www.ezmlm.org/

- qmail-autoresponder installed in /usr/local/bin/qmail-autoresponder 
   http://untroubled.org/qmail-autoresponder/ look for autoresponder link

Updates?
~~~~~~~~
 Latest version is available at:

 https://github.com/semhoun/qmailadmin


